      "content": "i get that, but it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine if there's no actual infection left to fight. like, if i feel totally healthy, isn't the goal accomplished? a lot of people say that if the symptoms are gone, the bacteria is gone too. is there really a big risk if i just stop now since it's already healed up?",
